H0.text: Fado is a type of music from which country. Portugal

H1.text: Fado is a type of music from which country. Spain

H2.text: Fado is a type of music from which country. Brazil

H3.text: Fado is a type of music from which country. Potiti

A4.text: Fado is a music genre which can be traced to the 1820s in Lisbon, Portugal, but probably has much earlier origins.

A5.text: It is one of two Portuguese music traditions part of the lists, the other being Cante Alentejano.
